00:16:32,950 --> 00:16:37,390
just say, for example, parties change, and it's no longer the same party that's managing

239
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:43,390
the agreement that executed it, so the intention isn't fully understood.

240
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:49,430
What is the cost of conflict in a contract disagreement after a contract's already

241
00:16:49,430 --> 00:16:50,430
been executed?

242
00:16:50,430 --> 00:16:56,350
When something goes wrong, and you see somebody, there's a perceived breach of contract, shall

