00:17:01,990 --> 00:17:05,750
He's not honest with me, I can't trust him, and immediately jump to that conclusion.

246
00:17:05,750 --> 00:17:10,110
And that becomes an emotional reaction, which typically triggers a call to your lawyer,

247
00:17:10,110 --> 00:17:14,310
or to your in-house counsel, and say, you've got to file a lawsuit.

