00:18:03,470 --> 00:18:12,190
So we don't try to sort of sit down and negotiate our differences, we go straight

262
00:18:12,190 --> 00:18:13,830
to battle.

263
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:19,750
Even if that was a case in international diplomacy, where diplomacy didn't work, and any time there

