00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:21,160
But I had to allow that to happen, as I say, just to allow some doubt and dissonance

373
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:24,240
to be introduced into that room.

374
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:29,600
And then what I did was I shifted it away completely from the legal side and started

375
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:33,160
going and trying to understand what the needs of the parties were, what were the concerns

376
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,400
of the parties.

